      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "Distinct weak layers exist in the old snowpack. This applies especially on west, north and east facing slopes. <br/> At high altitude the wind slabs have increased in size additionally in the last two days. The snowpack remains generally prone to triggering. <br/> Some snow will fall in particular in the regions of the north exposed to the foehn wind."
